议。记者实地探访了位于甘肃省白银市平川区水泉镇牙沟水村的「百万改造房」。对于网友对红砖房的质疑，当地村民有不同见解，年轻人认为红砖外墙符合当地建筑风格特色，年长的则认为不实用，但是对于价格都表示「不划算」。还有村民表示，感觉 100 多万的红砖房还不及自家五六万元的房子。对此，你怎么看？ [网页链接]"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-ecac5baf3630dcfacb1abf0fd839d59c_720w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "295 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/501407445"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ItfyT7Pz/oPx0EAMaCDczNzA0OTk1IMDD+4wGMCQ43QdAB3IJNTAxNDA3NDQ1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1637899392.1391299", "card_id": "Q_501197748", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 62}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "目前中国影史票房前五三部有吴京，吴京为什么能成为「票房密码」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-88bc6865e6273904689283a335172e9d_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "260 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/501197748"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4ItfyT7Pz/oPx0EAMaCDczNjU4NTU3IIDa9owGMAI4dUAIcgk1MDExOTc3NDh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1637899392.1395922", "card_id": "EV_12217647", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 0}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "蚂蚁金服招运营为什么要求 CPA 和 CFA 优先？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-31213a62725613eed6a2d9f3504d57a4_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "甄选福利"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/xen/market/training/promotion-activities/1447285831593144320"}}, "attached_info": "CpEBCLX8k+z8/6D8dBAYGgQ2MzMxIJr1/owGQAlyCDEyMjE3NjQ3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTKAVJodHRwczovL3d3dy56aGlodS5jb20veGVuL21hcmtldC90cmFpbmluZy9wcm9tb3Rpb24tYWN0aXZpdGllcy8xNDQ3Mjg1ODMxNTkzMTQ0MzIw8gEHCAESA3ZpcA=="}, {"type"